description:
*Lust of the Eyes (Part 2/3)* | Do your eyes tell you lies? Science tells us we often make quick moral judgments based on appearances, but often times those assumptions are incorrect. In this study, we will see how Jesus overcame when all kinds of visually appealing aspects of life were put in His path.
